================================= BetCalculator =================================
Authors: Albert Schaaf (281606)
		 Patrick Datko (281303)
=================================================================================
Setup
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Requirements

Java 6 (JDK1.6)
SBT 0.11+

===!===!===!===!===!===!===!=== ATTENTION ===!===!===!===!===!===!===!===!===!===!=
If an error occured during the compilation of the scala swing gui, it is possible
that you are not using a JDK1.6 or did not select this version.
Because of the changes in some classes of the native Swing Framework, some required
functions are disabled in JDK 1.7, which will be used by "peer"-method of scala
to get the native swing access.
===!===!===!===!===!===!===!===!===!===!===!===!===!===!===!===!===!===!===!===!===

Build
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------
In folder "Bet-Calculator"
$ sbt

$ compile -> Compile Source files
$ test -> Run all tests
$ run -> Compile and select UI (TUI/GUI/LIFT)

Lift Appendix:
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Before running lift, you have to start jetty. In sbt you can use following commands:
$ container:start -> Start jetty
$ container:stop -> Stops jetty
		